You are given a positive integer n. Find the sum of the numbers 1 + 2 + 3 + ... + n

Write a function called sum that takes n as an argument and returns the sum of the numbers 1 through n. Use a while loop when solving.

Examples:

sum (1) must return 1;
sum (2) must return 3;
sum (3) must return 6;
sum (10) must return 55.

Solution:

function sum(n){
let sum = n;
 while (n > 1) {
    n = n - 1;
    sum += n;
 }
 return sum;
}
